	<p><strong>Q: How will your pants affect my dancing?</strong></p>
<p>
A: Our pants help create perfect dance lines for you. The material that we use is thicker than normal business suit pants, which allows the pants to drape elegantly towards the floor. Our pants also stretch slightly allowing you greater and effortless movement.</p>
