<p><strong>Q: How do I figure out what size pants to order?</strong></p>
<p>A: Find a tape measure and wrap it snuggly around your waist (right above your hips!). Suck your stomach in slightly. Now measure. This is the waist size that you want to order.</p>
<br />
 
