<p><strong>Q: How do I wash my pants?</strong></p>
<p>A: Wash them cold and simply hang them up to dry to prevent wrinkles from forming. We would advise against putting them into a dryer. If you must iron them, iron them on a low heat setting.</p>
<br />
 
<p><strong>Q: What are your shipping options?</strong></p>
<p>A: We ship all our products using USPS priority mail. Shipping should take 2-3 business days to reach most places in the United States.</p>
<br />
 
<p><strong>Q: Will I need to alter these pants when I receive them?</strong></p>
<p>A: Yes, the only alteration needed will be the inseam as all our pants are shipped with a 38&quot; inseam. Simply take these pants into an alterations store and have them adjusted. Be sure to wear your dance shoes so that the store knows how much adjust the pants by.</p>
<br />
 
